{"tid":234452,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC免費千人版戰地風雲]PlanetSide 2","createTime":"2017-05-08T10:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T13:15:53.000Z","uid":114821,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d37a60827f3d90276b863c1c32b10d5b28089cc","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/218230/header.jpg?t=1472080110\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F218230%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1472080110&h=824e9c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">覺 唔 覺 BF 既 地 圖 好 細 ?<br />\n<br />\n搶 黎 搶 去 都 係 個 幾 點 好 悶 ?<br />\n<br />\n打 場 杖 咁 少 人 好 玩 咩 ! ! ! ?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n官網:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.planetside2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetside2.com%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4747ca66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.planetside2.com/</a> <br />\n(隻Game可以係Steam搵到並且下載)<br />\n<br />\n巴哈中文化:<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=20650&amp;snA=321&amp;tnum=22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D20650%26snA%3D321%26tnum%3D22&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=986e4376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=20650&amp;snA=321&amp;tnum=22</a> <br />\n(2015/3/3中文化更新) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">PlanetSide 2 是主打二十四小時無間斷的國家對戰射擊遊戲，殺了又殺，死了又死，考驗你射擊技巧，考驗你團體的默契 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n只係玩AU服 因為ping已經算係最低既一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得大家一齊玩<span style=\"color: purple;\">紫國</span>呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅國好多都係中國人</span> 定你想同佢地同一國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾段介紹片 望下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空戰<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/86eJLM0vUeo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F86eJLM0vUeo&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b11f83ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/86eJLM0vUeo</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/VGbzxRcvKRk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVGbzxRcvKRk&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bd79fee2\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/VGbzxRcvKRk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/_0U-G32X1dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_0U-G32X1dg&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9e907ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/_0U-G32X1dg</a><br />\n車戰<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/AVRbNezw46Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAVRbNezw46Q&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=86708eab\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/AVRbNezw46Q</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/AqT0URW197w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAqT0URW197w&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6481ad12\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/AqT0URW197w</a><br />\n步兵<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/1gYVYQYVNAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1gYVYQYVNAo&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=afabcc21\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/1gYVYQYVNAo</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/Fxf5xOctCq8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFxf5xOctCq8&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=36beafe8\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/Fxf5xOctCq8</a><br />\n搞笑<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/-hPkcvOyvg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-hPkcvOyvg0&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1eae5d4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/-hPkcvOyvg0</a>"},{"pid":"f6ba81bf1d4abbfa05e5402872a7840e19efd1f2","tid":234452,"uid":58950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"留名幫推"},{"pid":"db92cc70e453ddc05823325a98888c373522b36e","tid":234452,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"mac玩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee91fc89d4987c762dc5ac958ce6c130ef001381","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"成隻game唔係只有殺殺殺咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多工作要做<br />\n<br />\n‧ 大戰後佔領後需要搵人維修返破壞左既機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n‧ 採礦為自己國家[整一個屬於你個人既碉堡]<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/w7YpmoW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fw7YpmoW.png&h=bcc1b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DgPNp1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDgPNp1Q.png&h=2be6266c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lWz6H6N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlWz6H6N.png&h=de9ba100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eRYQAM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeRYQAM6.png&h=8af49b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n‧ 醫療當然唔洗講 戰場上最需要既兵種<br />\n‧ 子彈包無限供應 想玩幾耐都唔驚冇彈<br />\n<br />\n‧ 自己揸一部兵營車為隊友極速上返戰場<br />\n<br />\n之類仲有好多可以係隻game度搵到"},{"pid":"9d55900298f7f6f4a7a0a32714f029395bd63f98","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"坦克點止輕坦重坩咁單調<br />\n<br />\n等我話俾你知咩叫人型坦克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/M2s7kNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FM2s7kNI.jpg&h=5061c309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.g2a.com/m/1024x768/1x1x0/thumbnail/p/l/a72446a51961_planetside_2__1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.g2a.com%2Fm%2F1024x768%2F1x1x0%2Fthumbnail%2Fp%2Fl%2Fa72446a51961_planetside_2__1.jpg&h=c8b65cae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫車叫人型坦克都係屬於你私人<br />\n人地搶唔到你架車 (當然你都揸唔到人地部車啦,但照樣可以搭個順風車)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e192b0fcfe3b876e3415216980ae775d0c7f20fd","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"每個兵種都有唔同既<span style=\"color: gold;\">專屬技能</span><br />\n<br />\n而每個國家既兵種技能都一樣<br />\n<br />\n揀好兵種後點擊下圖位置<br />\n<br />\n就可以見到呢款兵種既專屬技能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VLDPAuQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVLDPAuQ.png&h=0f5ca8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫馨提示: F制係開技 唔好再問啦</span><br />\n<br />\n槍都有好多把 有分唔同既類型<br />\n入到game 自自然然睇得明架啦<br />\n<br />\n點數槍只不過係顏色唔同 冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a74843643330081a4f685e1b8a57817f267e32","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕介紹下俾新入門既玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狙擊手:</span></span><br />\nHunter Cloaking(遠狙必用)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zC9VJwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzC9VJwH.png&h=280f2750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消耗納米機械能量彎曲周圍既光線<br />\n造成<span style=\"color: red;\">近乎</span>完美的隱蔽性<br />\n解除隱形後隨住時間納米機械能量會補充<br />\n<br />\nNano-Armor Cloaking<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NPbBTpw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNPbBTpw.png&h=c195f2e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開技將減少35%來自<span style=\"color: red;\">子彈類武器</span>的傷害<br />\n(個人黎講覺得好垃圾 用都沒用過)<br />\n<br />\nStalker Cloaking(刺客流)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OheqcR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOheqcR7.png&h=cb4518cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣係隱形 但唔郁就唔會消耗能量<br />\n甚至係會回復能量<br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">禁止裝備主要武器</span>(即係你冇你把大狙用!)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">輕型突種兵:</span></span><br />\nJump Jets<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/D5gYeDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FD5gYeDd.png&h=13d23bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傳說中既<span style=\"color: red;\">噴射器</span> 去屋企去山頂陰人零難度<br />\n<br />\nDrifter Jump Jets<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/C0xEyb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FC0xEyb0.png&h=ac45619b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">滑翔</span>噴射器<br />\n<br />\nIcarus Jump Jets<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Pqm110f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPqm110f.png&h=4e4d5f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火箭噴射器 只有<span style=\"color: red;\">向上快</span> 各方位會增加消耗能量"},{"pid":"6c263e068d9a1bfa5beb71458703b7cd220ad24a","tid":234452,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"玩過留名"},{"pid":"1af041de03e816f4a1d6c38cde8cf0e1a225902a","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"點解BF1就咁多人玩<br />\n明明多野玩過BF 又好玩過BF<br />\n係畫質冇佢咁靚<br />\n<br />\n可以除時關game既打仗遊戲 邊度搵"},{"pid":"7e042a1040bfb7418dc2d590e9d4d1440d1cfc45","tid":234452,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T18:05:46.000Z","msg":"聽日研究下"},{"pid":"cb7dcb4396b340c5046d5e3ecafda6505b1f6b25","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,