t;漢化腳本.bat&quot;<br />\n3.等他複製完成後按任務鍵<br />\n4.進入遊戲,如正常顯示中文字即代表漢化成功!~<br />\n<br />\n腳本路徑預設為&quot;C:\\Program Files\\PlanetSide 2&quot;<br />\n如果你的遊戲安裝位置不是在這個路徑,請自己修改!<br />\n遊戲路徑可以從 登入器 &gt; 按右鍵 &gt; 按內容 &gt; 目標 看到<br />\n然後把&quot;漢化腳本.bat&quot; 按右鍵 &gt; 編輯 &gt; 修改內容即可!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSTEAM版的路徑可以從 遊戲 &gt; 右鍵 &gt;內容 &gt;本機檔案 &gt; 瀏覽本機檔案中<br />\n找到遊戲路徑<br />\n視乎你的STEAM裝在那個盤,沒更改過預設路徑的話,<br />\n大概就是以下(請自行改回自己遊戲路徑的英文)<br />\nC:\\Program Files\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\PlanetSide 2"},{"pid":"156bdec92d8c991fe6b959581522aa8e0dbb4c8b","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎黎黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2017/4/21 最新漢化包</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!FgUTTRzR!dH-P3skyko9CPwyK7xQnXga4b2JHAwHDasdw6OPkamA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21FgUTTRzR%21dH-P3skyko9CPwyK7xQnXga4b2JHAwHDasdw6OPkamA&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9UzxzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e1a3e718\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!FgUTTRzR!dH-P3skyko9CPwyK7xQnXga4b2JHAwHDasdw6OPkamA</a><br />\n<br />\n【教學:】<br />\n<br />\n1.下載壓縮檔,然後解壓縮<br />\n2.打開遊戲登入器,再打開&quot;漢化腳本.bat&quot;<br />\n3.等他複製完成後按任務鍵<br />\n4.進入遊戲,如正常顯示中文字即代表漢化成功!~<br />\n<br />\n腳本路徑預設為&quot;C:\\Program Files\\PlanetSide 2&quot;<br />\n如果你的遊戲安裝位置不是在這個路徑,請自己修改!<br />\n遊戲路徑可以從 登入器 &gt; 按右鍵 &gt; 按內容 &gt; 目標 看到<br />\n然後把&quot;漢化腳本.bat&quot; 按右鍵 &gt; 編輯 &gt; 修改內容即可!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSTEAM版的路徑可以從 遊戲 &gt; 右鍵 &gt;內容 &gt;本機檔案 &gt; 瀏覽本機檔案中<br />\n找到遊戲路徑<br />\n視乎你的STEAM裝在那個盤,沒更改過預設路徑的話,<br />\n大概就是以下(請自行改回自己遊戲路徑的英文)<br />\nC:\\Program Files\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\PlanetSide 2</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每次開game更新完 , 都要<span style=\"color: green;\">重開</span>一次漢化包</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為遊戲官方登陸器<span style=\"color: red;\">【每次】</span>登陸賬號後，會校驗客戶端文件完整性，並<span style=\"color: red;\">【修復】</span>任何修改過的文件，包括因漢化而修改的語言文件</span>"},{"pid":"cb71d3e234bad879f4d116ecb0e7dc5298651c7b","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"下次我開post會將呢段野再綜合下 唔好意思"},{"pid":"5af83db9125aa931117206791096272fae8e92ea","tid":234452,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"569a8e2120cb875434253576e3295049a6b9c959","tid":234452,"uid":39178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Promote planetside咪 promote  planetside lo<br />\n踩battlefield 又有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比較都叫踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:1942玩到而家BF1都有玩<br />\nplanetside2係大型戰方面確係比較好<br />\nBF系列就畫面比較好，較真實，但BF3開始比較著重個人，團隊合作比較少<br />\n就算而家BF1有幾多人肯做醫療兵就知</blockquote><br />\n你利申果啲就叫比較啦<br />\n上面果啲（又唔明bf1多人玩，多野過bf，好玩過bf）<br />\n都唔叫踩啊？"},{"pid":"53665e3c330f2b84b327e7d12653387a8970f453","tid":234452,"uid":76473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:13:43.000Z","msg":"呢隻舊game冇人想玩 仲要前期投入勁多時間賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fb64f15925a7a33d831611bfa1ed9eafd94b63","tid":234452,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻舊game冇人想玩 仲要前期投入勁多時間賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家頭14個lv送100cert point 解成就又有<br />\n低lv有技術可以屌打下120lv<br />\n琴日團戰一直用紫國支heavy gun超遠距離同滲透打 佢狙唔到我又比我磨血磨走 仲可以殺下佢身邊d人仔"},{"pid":"a98b9edd07ea5081c39bc474ed8a4f3c4514e81c","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Promote planetside咪 promote  planetside lo<br />\n踩battlefield 又有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比較都叫踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:1942玩到而家BF1都有玩<br />\nplanetside2係大型戰方面確係比較好<br />\nBF系列就畫面比較好，較真實，但BF3開始比較著重個人，團隊合作比較少<br />\n就算而家BF1有幾多人肯做醫療兵就知</blockquote><br />\n你利申果啲就叫比較啦<br />\n上面果啲（又唔明bf1多人玩，多野過bf，好玩過bf）<br />\n都唔叫踩啊？</blockquote><br />\n我錯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry 想吸引啲ja"},{"pid":"e681366fea2037b361663d5f5e0523b3df27a812","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻舊game冇人想玩 仲要前期投入勁多時間賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺得有個賺錢既目標<br />\n同埋後期可以買呢樣買個樣然後升級自己<br />\n好有目標既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知呀 覺得係一種動推力"},{"pid":"0ead5a8c2cd24bf8c4de7cd61d6ffc2bcf0d9462","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢隻舊game冇人想玩 仲要前期投入勁多時間賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家頭14個lv送100cert point 解成就又有<br />\n低lv有技術可以屌打下120lv<br />\n琴日團戰一直用紫國支heavy gun超遠距離同滲透打 佢狙唔到我又比我磨血磨走 仲可以殺下佢身邊d人仔</blockquote><br />\n可能尋日同你同場過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾點打"},{"pid":"7f0752952c6d2105851b8eecab1d4dc9b3d6b220","tid":234452,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfd5c9a3216e5ad530bbb2f57b623cb57d62aa6","tid":234452,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"新手建議咩都玩下 唔好淨做工程 醫療兵<br />\n有cert point留返 唔好晒 投資落你最上手既兵到<br />\n藍國滲透一開始把狙係單發 打頭可秒<br />\n紅紫國一開始果把係連發 打頭2下 身3下<br />\n玩得熟 連發比單發好用<br />\n如果玩滲透 請善用f 技能隱形（隱形打唔到人）<br />\n<br />\n輕突 工程一開始果把卡賓殺人都好用<br />\n（我用紅國果把好快拎左紫牌（殺1260人））<br />\n輕突機動性高又可以飛（space)<br />\n新手玩輕突都可以練槍技術 再配c4 係人群上面放c4再炸 人頭好拎<br />\n<br />\n0課唔建議玩max 雖然血厚 但要有合作先有用 再者 max通常針對單一樣野（打人/打max/打載具）先會有好好效果 但雙手同武就要用cert point/課金買另一隻手既武器<br />\n<br />\n重突 係戰場上都以1挑多既情況下可以打贏 同輕突分別就係唔可以飛 但甲比較厚 技能都係甲<br />\n重突建議中期先開始投資certpoint升<br />\n因為重突用certpoint比較多 但呢隻game技術，經驗比lv重要  所以做投資重突既可以慢慢黎"},{"pid":"fcc9515db0fac2c81e43d6ef2bfdfbcd178aa0e6","tid":234452,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1a68d040b7a5c3cbc3e6010f7c2900378e4c17b7","tid":234452,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢隻舊game冇人想玩 仲要前期投入勁多時間賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家頭14個lv送100cert point 解成就又有<br />\n低lv有技術可以屌打下120lv<br />\n琴日團戰一直用紫國支heavy gun超遠距離同滲透打 佢狙唔到我又比我磨血磨走 仲可以殺下佢身邊d人仔</blockquote><br />\n可能尋日同你同場過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾點打</blockquote><br />\n我放工打 8-11啦 依排打鳩藍國班中國人<br />\n成日打HHCN<br />\n仲好似多左個AY咩野既軍團又係多中國人"},{"pid":"dba1aa30552d1e6d4aa9e11e7a6d9f3e5cc5125b","tid":234452,"uid":27381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"前舊登成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前十幾條友一齊衝好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bfc655bada3777214a804743c06ad7ad8ef8ba","tid":234452,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"開咗可以打CELL打剩就無玩"},{"pid":"38dadc9330530c1f75dbff33287c27142aa085a7","tid":234452,"uid":114821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"點解個個都鐘意玩紅藍國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e02a5d6584576e4c6ced32e0b0f58a90782bed","tid":234452,"uid":24962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep